snippet.title: LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/lego-star-wars-the-skywalker-saga-switch/

Play through all nine Skywalker Saga films in a brand-new LEGO video game unlike any other. Experience fun-filled adventures, whimsical humor, and the freedom to fully immerse yourself in the LEGO Star Wars galaxy.

#LEGOStarWarsGame #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
